ZH: 我每天早上喝一杯牛奶。
EN: I drink a glass of milk every morning.

ZH: 你喜欢喝牛奶吗？
EN: Do you like to drink milk?

ZH: 她用牛奶做了一杯热巧克力。
EN: She made a hot chocolate with milk.

ZH: 孩子们每天都喝牛奶。
EN: The children drink milk every day.

ZH: 牛奶是很好的营养来源。
EN: Milk is a good source of nutrition.

ZH: 我在超市买了一大瓶牛奶。
EN: I bought a large bottle of milk at the supermarket.

ZH: 妈妈常常给我做牛奶麦片。
EN: Mom often makes me milk and cereal.

ZH: 牛奶有助于骨骼的生长。
EN: Milk helps with bone growth.

ZH: 老人说喝牛奶有利于健康。
EN: The elderly say that drinking milk is good for health.

ZH: 这里有一块奶酪和一杯牛奶。
EN: There is a piece of cheese and a glass of milk here.

ZH: 我们家每周都会订牛奶送货。
EN: Our family subscribes to milk delivery every week.

ZH: 牛奶可以加热也可以冷饮。
EN: Milk can be served hot or cold.

ZH: 这家店有各种各样的牛奶产品。
EN: This store has a variety of milk products.

ZH: 我无法喝牛奶，因为对它过敏。
EN: I cannot drink milk because I am allergic to it.

ZH: 牛奶是我早餐必不可少的一部分。
EN: Milk is an essential part of my breakfast.

ZH: 我买的牛奶是有机的，没有添加物。
EN: The milk I bought is organic and free from additives.

ZH: 我的猫喜欢喝牛奶。
EN: My cat likes to drink milk.

ZH: 牛奶可以被用来制造奶酪和酸奶。
EN: Milk can be used to make cheese and yogurt.

ZH: 我一天喝两杯牛奶，以保持健康。
EN: I drink two cups of milk a day to stay healthy.

ZH: 奶奶说每晚喝一杯牛奶可以帮助入睡。
EN: Grandma says that drinking a glass of milk every night can help with sleep.
